data.title: Dinah Shore Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Dinah Shore on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Dinah Shore including Fun and Fancy Free, Oh, God!, and more.
data.text:
Alma Murder

A former sorority sister (Dinah Shore) asks Jessica's (Angela Lansbury) help in clearing the name of a respected college professor (E.G. Marshall) who has confessed to murder. Ralph Waite also guest stars.

Someone's On the Ski Lift with Dinah

Lucy gets the same ski lift chair with her favorite star, Dinah Shore, and just about ruins Dinah's alpine vacation.

Mel's in the Kitchen with Dinah

Mel (VIC TAYBACK) is invited to prepare his famous chili on "The Dinah Shore Show," and the girls all want to go too.

Dinah Shore

"I saw it in the window, and I just couldn't resist it." One of the show's finest hours, the hilarious spoof "Went With The Wind!" is presented here for your entertainment. Dinah Shore guest stars.
